<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="advance-v">advance <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əd'vɑːns/    美 /əd'væns/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(尤指士兵) 前进；向前移动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The army <strong>advanced across</strong> the plain. 
军队前进穿过平原。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(使) 进展；(使) 进步：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have advanced greatly / significantly / considerably in our knowledge of the universe.
我们对宇宙的认识取得了很大的进步。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This research has done much to advance our understanding of language learning. 
这项研究非常有助于我们提高对语言学习的认识。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(时间) 提前；(价格) 上涨；预支 (钱)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The date of the meeting was advanced from July 10 to July 1. 
会议日期已从7月10日提早到7月1日。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are willing to advance the money to you / advance you the money.
我们愿意把钱预支给你。</p></div>

<h4 id="4further">4.<strong>促进；推动(further):</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She decided to go back to college to advance her career.
为了促进职业的发展，她决定回到大学（继续学习）。</p><footer>2020 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>提出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>advance an idea / a theory / a plan
提出想法 / 理论 / 计划</p></div></div>